# Task Manager - Environment Configuration

## Server Environment Variables
Copy these to `server/.env` and customize as needed.

```
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key_change_in_production
PORT=4000
DATABASE_FILE=./models/dev.sqlite
NODE_ENV=development
```

## Client Environment Variables (optional)
Create `client/.env` to override the API base URL (default: `/api` via Vite proxy)

```
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:4000/api
```
